<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْفَصْل الثَّانِي فِي تَعْرِيف السَّنَد والمتن وعوارضهما<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>السَّنَد<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>السَّنَد طَرِيق الحَدِيث وَهُوَ رِجَاله الَّذين رَوَوْهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الْإِسْنَاد<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>والإسناد بِمَعْنَاهُ وَقد يجيىء بِمَعْنى ذكر السَّنَد والحكاية عَن طَرِيق الْمَتْن<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>الْمَتْن<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مَا انْتهى إِلَيْهِ الْإِسْنَاد<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>